Package Assignment

Class Database

java.lang.Object
Assignment.Database
public class Database extends Object
Database containing Student list, Faculty list, Project list and FYPCoordinator list. It uses the helper class Excel to read and write data files.
Since:
2023-04-10
Version:
1.0
